Title: A Girl Called Jules
Writer: Marcello Coscia, Bruno Di Geronimo, Mauro Di Nardo, Francesco Mazzei, Milena Milani (novel), Tonino Valerii
Actors: Silvia Dionisio, Gianni Macchia, Esmeralda Ruspoli, Tonino Valerii
Plot: Teen girl Jules must deal with her budding sexuality, and the fact that some men and women want her adds to her confusion.
